{"tid":1950286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關閉邊界前抵美國  川普：不會支付哈利與梅根的安全費用","createTime":"2020-03-30T08:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T09:35:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac91efaea0b6ed81d0fde76167b9dbd6f5b0658e","tid":1950286,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZK525n7oGAMCIy.GJDTnhg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzYw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/rti.org.tw/388e9cea790d23a6e7532afb5e78bdea\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZK525n7oGAMCIy.GJDTnhg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzYw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Frti.org.tw%2F388e9cea790d23a6e7532afb5e78bdea&h=9d722174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普29日表示，美國不會支付英國王子哈利(Prince Harry)及其妻子梅根(Meghan)的安全費用。川普的說法證實了這對英國皇室夫婦已經移居到美國加州。<br />\n<br />\n美國和加拿大的邊界已經因為俗稱武漢肺炎的2019年冠狀病毒疾病(COVID-19)疫情而關閉。根據媒體報導，哈利夫婦趕在邊界關閉前，搭乘私人飛機從加拿大飛抵美國洛杉磯。<br />\n<br />\n哈利夫婦已經居住在加拿大數個月。在此之前，他們在今年初宣布，將不再代表王室執行公務，將追求自己的嶄新、獨立的生活，引發英國王室的軒然大波。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">川普29日在推特上說：「我是英國女王和英國的最好朋友及景仰者。據報導，離開英國的哈利和梅根，將永久居住在加拿大。現在，他們已經離開加拿大到美國，但，美國將不會支持他們的安全保護。他們必須自己付錢！」</span><br />\n<br />\n美國籍的梅根在洛杉磯長大，而她的母親拉格蘭(Doria Ragland)仍居住在這個城市。演員出生的梅根在洛杉磯有許多朋友和工作合約。她將在此地重新發展事業。<br />\n<br />\n迪士尼公司在26日宣布，梅根將在一部描述非洲大象家族的新電影中演出。<br />\n<br />\n根據媒體報導，哈利最近曾遭詐騙電話錄音。在電話中，他抨擊川普對環境變遷的立場。錄音檔上傳YouTube後曝光，哈利被網友狂酸智商低。<br />\n<br />\n哈利和梅根將在3月31日正式卸下高階王室成員身分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%93%88%E5%88%A9%E8%88%87%E6%A2%85%E6%A0%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%B2%BB%E7%94%A8-231453733.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B7%259D%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2594%25AF%25E4%25BB%2598%25E5%2593%2588%25E5%2588%25A9%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25A2%2585%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E7%2594%25A8-231453733.html&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2R4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=e6d83b9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%93%88%E5%88%A9%E8%88%87%E6%A2%85%E6%A0%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E8%B2%BB%E7%94%A8-231453733.html</a>"},{"pid":"0c8d60ab94c28027ccd6c53bd515887aefb9ff72","tid":1950286,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"梅根條臭西唔係話TRUMP唔落台都唔去美國咩"},{"pid":"c90cca3dcd42f48ebb226a516c31868334214a21","tid":1950286,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c8d60ab94c28027ccd6c53bd515887aefb9ff72","tid":1950286,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"梅根條臭西唔係話TRUMP唔落台都唔去美國咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:32:07.000Z","msg":"口裡說不"},{"pid":"4ce31ead50f29ffacba44007aa106c2c25917bfd","tid":1950286,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:35:03.000Z","msg":"個個都係侵既好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}